{"title":"伞","authors":["宁松勋"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁松勋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友送给我一把纸伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是泸州有名的特产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收拢，一柄闪光的利剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撑开，一朵盛开的花瓣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“烈日见它退避，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风见它躲闪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕是暴雨袭来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它也拚命抵拦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外表诚然美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禀性钢一样勇敢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像我们泸州人的性格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕任何困难！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记朋友的话语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伞啊，掀起我心中的波澜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要带它远行万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走荒原，入深山……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}